{"thi-ap35:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap35:0.2":"Khattiyavagga ","thi-ap35:0.3":"Sukkatheriapadana ","thi-ap35:1.1":"“Ekanavutito kappe, ","thi-ap35:1.2":"vipassi nama nayako; ","thi-ap35:1.3":"Uppajji carudassano, ","thi-ap35:1.4":"sabbadhammavipassako. ","thi-ap35:2.1":"Tadaham bandhumatiyam, ","thi-ap35:2.2":"jata annatare kule; ","thi-ap35:2.3":"Dhammam sutvana munino, ","thi-ap35:2.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap35:3.1":"Bahussuta dhammadhara, ","thi-ap35:3.2":"patibhanavati tatha; ","thi-ap35:3.3":"Vicittakathika capi, ","thi-ap35:3.4":"jinasasanakarika. ","thi-ap35:4.1":"Tada dhammakatham katva, ","thi-ap35:4.2":"hitaya janatam bahum; ","thi-ap35:4.3":"Tato cutaham tusitam, ","thi-ap35:4.4":"upapanna yasassini. ","thi-ap35:5.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","thi-ap35:5.2":"sikhi viya sikhi jino; ","thi-ap35:5.3":"Tapanto yasasa loke, ","thi-ap35:5.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap35:6.1":"Tadapi pabbajitvana, ","thi-ap35:6.2":"buddhasasanakovida; ","thi-ap35:6.3":"Jotetva jinavakyani, ","thi-ap35:6.4":"tatopi tidivam gata. ","thi-ap35:7.1":"Ekattimseva kappamhi, ","thi-ap35:7.2":"vessabhu nama nayako; ","thi-ap35:7.3":"Uppajjittha mahanani, ","thi-ap35:7.4":"tadapi ca tathevaham. ","thi-ap35:8.1":"Pabbajitva dhammadhara, ","thi-ap35:8.2":"jotayim jinasasanam; ","thi-ap35:8.3":"Gantva marupuram rammam, ","thi-ap35:8.4":"anubhosim mahasukham. ","thi-ap35:9.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap35:9.2":"kakusandho jinuttamo; ","thi-ap35:9.3":"Uppajji narasarano, ","thi-ap35:9.4":"tadapi ca tathevaham. ","thi-ap35:10.1":"Pabbajitva munimatam, ","thi-ap35:10.2":"jotayitva yathayukam; ","thi-ap35:10.3":"Tato cutaham tidivam, ","thi-ap35:10.4":"agam sabhavanam yatha. ","thi-ap35:11.1":"Imasmimyeva kappamhi, ","thi-ap35:11.2":"konagamananayako; ","thi-ap35:11.3":"Uppajji lokasarano, ","thi-ap35:11.4":"arano amatangato. ","thi-ap35:12.1":"Tadapi pabbajitvana, ","thi-ap35:12.2":"sasane tassa tadino; ","thi-ap35:12.3":"Bahussuta dhammadhara, ","thi-ap35:12.4":"jotayim jinasasanam. ","thi-ap35:13.1":"Imasmimyeva kappamhi, ","thi-ap35:13.2":"kassapo munimuttamo; ","thi-ap35:13.3":"Uppajji lokasarano, ","thi-ap35:13.4":"arano maranantagu. ","thi-ap35:14.1":"Tassapi naravirassa, ","thi-ap35:14.2":"pabbajitvana sasane; ","thi-ap35:14.3":"Pariyaputasaddhamma, ","thi-ap35:14.4":"paripuccha visarada. ","thi-ap35:15.1":"Susila lajjini ceva, ","thi-ap35:15.2":"tisu sikkhasu kovida; ","thi-ap35:15.3":"Bahum dhammakatham katva, ","thi-ap35:15.4":"yavajivam mahamune. ","thi-ap35:16.1":"Tena kammavipakena, ","thi-ap35:16.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap35:16.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap35:16.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap35:17.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap35:17.2":"giribbajapuruttame; ","thi-ap35:17.3":"Jata setthikule phite, ","thi-ap35:17.4":"maharatanasancaye. ","thi-ap35:18.1":"Yada bhikkhusahassena, ","thi-ap35:18.2":"parivuto lokanayako; ","thi-ap35:18.3":"Upagami rajagaham, ","thi-ap35:18.4":"sahassakkhena vannito. ","thi-ap35:19.1":"Danto dantehi saha puranajatilehi, ","thi-ap35:19.2":"Vippamutto vippamuttehi; ","thi-ap35:19.3":"Singinikkhasavanno, ","thi-ap35:19.4":"Rajagaham pavisi bhagava. ","thi-ap35:20.1":"Disva buddhanubhavam tam, ","thi-ap35:20.2":"sutvava gunasancayam; ","thi-ap35:20.3":"Buddhe cittam pasadetva, ","thi-ap35:20.4":"pujayim tam yathabalam. ","thi-ap35:21.1":"Aparena ca kalena, ","thi-ap35:21.2":"dhammadinnaya santike; ","thi-ap35:21.3":"Agara nikkhamitvana, ","thi-ap35:21.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap35:22.1":"Kesesu chijjamanesu, ","thi-ap35:22.2":"kilese jhapayim aham; ","thi-ap35:22.3":"Uggahim sasanam sabbam, ","thi-ap35:22.4":"pabbajitva cirenaham. ","thi-ap35:23.1":"Tato dhammamadesesim, ","thi-ap35:23.2":"mahajanasamagame; ","thi-ap35:23.3":"Dhamme desiyamanamhi, ","thi-ap35:23.4":"dhammabhisamayo ahu. ","thi-ap35:24.1":"Nekapanasahassanam, ","thi-ap35:24.2":"tam viditvativimhito; ","thi-ap35:24.3":"Abhippasanno me yakkho, ","thi-ap35:24.4":"bhamitvana giribbajam. ","thi-ap35:25.1":"Kim me kata rajagahe manussa, ","thi-ap35:25.2":"Madhum pitava acchare; ","thi-ap35:25.3":"Ye sukkam na upasanti, ","thi-ap35:25.4":"Desentim amatam padam. ","thi-ap35:26.1":"Tanca appativaniyam, ","thi-ap35:26.2":"asecanakamojavam; ","thi-ap35:26.3":"Pivanti manne sappanna, ","thi-ap35:26.4":"valahakamivaddhagu. ","thi-ap35:27.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap35:27.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap35:27.3":"Cetopariyananassa, ","thi-ap35:27.4":"vasi homi mahamune. ","thi-ap35:28.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap35:28.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap35:28.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap35:28.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap35:29.1":"Atthadhammaniruttisu, ","thi-ap35:29.2":"patibhane tatheva ca; ","thi-ap35:29.3":"Nanam mama mahavira, ","thi-ap35:29.4":"uppannam tava santike. ","thi-ap35:30.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap35:30.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap35:30.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap35:31.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap35:31.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap35:31.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap35:32.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap35:32.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap35:32.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap35:33.1":"Ittham sudam sukka bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap35:34.1":"Sukkatheriyapadanam pancamam. ","thi-ap35:34.2":"Pancamam bhanavaram. "}